{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "20428 2042803",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "精灵梅奈是养育伊莉雅长大的监护人。\\n她的这份爱超越了种族。塞西娅开始意识到\\n这个世界虽然和自己所了解的历史\\n截然不同，但依然有值得守护的事物。\\n而伊莉雅则看穿了塞西娅的真实身份。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "距今约1000年前，\\n炼金术的发展日新月异，\\n人类的繁荣也日益兴盛，\\n终于建立起高度的钢铁文明。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "人类过上了安稳舒适的生活。\\n却为此破坏了自然，\\n扰乱了魔力。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "自然与魔法的紊乱\\n侵蚀着龙的躯体，\\n甚至剥夺了龙的生命。\\n最终，人与龙开始了惨烈的战争。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "人龙之战，激烈无比。\\n这场看不到尽头的战争旷日持久，\\n最终，\\n人类率先打开了潘多拉的魔盒。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "为了战胜龙，\\n人类打造出通往异界之门的钥匙，\\n从异界的彼端召来了灾厄。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "然而，灾厄并没有成为\\n人类的伙伴。\\n对于灾厄来说，不分人与龙，\\n只是破坏一切、毁灭一切，\\n令世界充满绝望。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "人类从世界尽头召唤而来的灾厄……\\n不知何时起，\\n被称作了魔神。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "有一头龙忧心于魔神导致的\\n秩序崩塌，\\n那便是圣域龙，\\n掌管光之力，\\n是龙之中最伟大的存在。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "圣域龙选择了一位怀瑾握瑜的人类，\\n与其缔结了契约。\\n那正是巫女的始祖，伊莉雅。\\n被后世尊为女神之人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "伊莉雅与圣域龙一同\\n奔走游说，\\n主张只有人与龙重归于好，\\n才能拥有与魔神抗衡之力。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "人们在她们身上看到了希望，\\n人与龙齐心协力，经历一场殊死战斗，\\n终于成功封印了魔神。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "从此，\\n人类舍弃了过度发展的文明，\\n决心与龙共存。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "这便是伊莉雅史的开端，\\n“第一次封魔战争”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "这就是我所了解的历史……\\n但感觉现在所处的过去世界\\n和我了解的历史截然不同。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我为伊莉雅提供\\n研究所使用的魔力，\\n相对地，我可以在她家借住。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "来到这个时代已有些时日，\\n但我依然对自己\\n应该做什么感到迷茫……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "伊莉雅，什么是爱？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这问题很难回答。\\n每个人都有不同的理解，\\n并没有标准答案哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "爱是……\\n没有答案的东西吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "是啊，总有一天\\n你会找到属于自己的答案。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "（伊莉雅还有莫尔提斯……\\n这个世界有别于我所了解的历史。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "（如果我和伊莉雅的相遇\\n导致历史被改写了，\\n那就得尽可能地修正才行。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "（不然，对未来也会有影响。\\n我和哥哥甚至可能根本不会\\n降生于世。但是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "你一脸凝重呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "梅奈……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "伊莉雅和莫尔提斯\\n已经彻底熟稔了。看那样子，\\n现在也没法让他们分开……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "之前梅奈反对\\n把莫尔提斯留在这里吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "是啊，龙和精灵不怎么喜欢\\n来自异界的东西。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "现在人与龙纷争不断，\\n我不希望她留下\\n可能成为导火索的东西……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "而且，异界之物都是未知数。\\n要是他会伤害\\n我最珍视的伊莉雅……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "呵呵，我记得\\n伊莉雅是你养大的吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "是啊。在她还是婴儿时，\\n她的母亲就把她托付给我了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "我因为和伊莉雅的相遇而改变了。\\n现在她对于我来说是最重要的存在，\\n所以我总是对她过度保护……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "不过呢，担心归担心，\\n但在莫尔提斯这件事上\\n我还是有些欣慰的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "伊莉雅讨厌与人相处，\\n至今为止都不怎么\\n和我以外的他人接触。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "不过她和莫尔提斯\\n还有你都处得不错呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "有莫尔提斯在的话，\\n就算以后我不在了，\\n伊莉雅也不会觉得寂寞了吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "诶？你不在是指……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "精灵族有个习俗，\\n青年时期的精灵\\n身体会变大一段时间……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "这时才能第一次走出王国，\\n去了解外面的世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "之后身体会变回原来的大小，\\n那时候就得回国……\\n再也不能踏出国门半步。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "那就是说……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "没错。等那一天到来，\\n我就得和伊莉雅说再见了。\\n而那一天随时有可能到来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "只要伊莉雅能开心，\\n我就满足了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "梅奈……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "（如果要让这个世界\\n照我所了解的历史发展，\\n魔神就得被召唤出来才行。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "（但那会导致世界的毁灭。\\n这个时代明明也有\\n值得守护的事物……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "（不惜毁灭一切召唤魔神，\\n真的是对的吗？）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "（我该相信什么，\\n又该保护什么呢……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "女神伊莉雅啊，\\n请指引我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "啊，塞西娅，你在这里啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "伊莉雅……有什么事吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我有事想问你，我这人\\n有在意的事就坐不住。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我就直说了吧。\\n你不是这个世界的人吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我为了炼成\\n通往异界之门的钥匙，\\n一直在进行异界相关的研究。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "然后呢，开启门的那天，\\n我的秘密基地之外的地方\\n出现了异界反应。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "除了炼金术以外，\\n其它好多这个时代的常识\\n你也不知道。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你总是对我们客客气气的，\\n也不打算挑明自己的身份……\\n一直在隐瞒着什么。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "所以我做出了这个猜测……\\n你来自别的世界，\\n然后进入森林遇到了我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你之所以阻止我开启门，\\n是因为你知道\\n那之后的世界发生了什么。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你来自未来的世界……\\n我这个猜测如何？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "就算你的猜测是对的，\\n你又打算怎么处置我？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_03_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "诶？没什么打算。\\n我就是想来对个答案而已。",
